Setting up things
========================================================

```{r}
# To parse XML documents
library(XBRL)
old_o <- options(stringsAsFactors = FALSE)
# To visualize results
library(plotly)
library(ggplot2)
# To analyze balance sheets
library(finstr)
# Data munging
library(dplyr)

# Setting Workspace
setwd("~/Work/BigDataAssignments/secgovanalyze")
```

